social_posts.post_text: All this snow makes for good days on the hill. Hope everyone else had a terrific new years weekend #sustainable #sungrowncannabis #cleangreen #snowfarming

Who has tried our live hash rosin? Were pretty hyped on it ourselves. Shout out to @knots.cannabis for making it for us and @faded.flat.four for showcasing it! We appreciate you guys. #sustainable #sungrowncannabis #cleangreen #notill #livingsoil #lightdep #singlesource #rosin #applezauce #mimosazkittlez #lazybee 🐝

Try getting work done with these turkeys at you feet lol #distractions #lazybees

The new momma’s are growing up nicely and cloning season is closing in. Its all about to kick off again for another season and we are pretty excited to get at it. #timeflies #sustainable #sungrowncannabis #cleangreen #moms #cloneseason #lazybee 🐝
